"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-08-07-team-gb-star-george-mills-fights-french-rival-falling-olympic-5000m-race-21376153\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Team GB's George Mills was furious with his French rival Hugo Hay after a fall in their Olympic 5000m qualifier on Wednesday morning.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 133, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 7, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9694783023879916, \"rank\": 0.025378913616446154, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_2012_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On the final straight of the first heat at the Stade de France, Mills was at the centre of a collision with Hay, which also brought down three other athletes.\", \"from\": 135, \"to\": 293, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Mills, the son of formerLeeds Unitedand England defender Danny Mills, was livid as he walked across the finish line and immediately confronted Hay.\", \"from\": 295, \"to\": 442, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 335, \"end\": 342, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999962741932281, \"rank\": 2.228314473044381e-06, \"text\": \"England\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 352, \"end\": 363, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Danny_Mills\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.516065700023937e-24, \"text\": \"Danny Mills\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Danny_Mills\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Danny_Mills\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Frenchman, who finished seventh, attempted to diffuse the situation as Mills approached and pointed a finger in his face.\", \"from\": 444, \"to\": 569, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The pair exchanged words but Mills did not appear to be satisfied with Hay's response as he brushed the Frenchman's hand off his shoulder as he walked away.\", \"from\": 571, \"to\": 727, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Earlier in the race, Canada's Mohamed Ahmed had also fallen in a tightly packed field.\", \"from\": 729, \"to\": 815, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 750, \"end\": 756, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"score\": 0.7107547360149435, \"rank\": 0.34526828378020746, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\"}, {\"begin\": 759, \"end\": 772, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mohamed_Ahmed_(Comorian_politician)\", \"score\": 0.639998145003644, \"rank\": 0.5624999999999292, \"text\": \"Mohamed Ahmed\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mohamed_Ahmed_(Comorian_politician)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mohamed_Ahmed_(Comorian_politician)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But the major flashpoint came in the final 100 metres of the race when Mills attempted to run beside Hay but was blocked by the Frenchman.\", \"from\": 817, \"to\": 955, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Mills quickly lost balance and tumbled to the track, taking the Netherlands' Mike Foppen, Spain's Thierry Ndikumwenayo and the Refugee Team's Dominic Lokinyomo Lobalu down with him.\", \"from\": 957, \"to\": 1138, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1021, \"end\": 1032, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9989045625683415, \"rank\": 0.0010370288288320008, \"text\": \"Netherlands\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1047, \"end\": 1052, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999825872693, \"rank\": 1.2015916835179991e-08, \"text\": \"Spain\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1055, \"end\": 1075, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thierry_Ndikumwenayo\", \"score\": 0.9999987278196293, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Thierry Ndikumwenayo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thierry_Ndikumwenayo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thierry_Ndikumwenayo\"}, {\"begin\": 1084, \"end\": 1096, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Refugee_Olympic_Team_at_the_2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Refugee Team\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Refugee_Olympic_Team_at_the_2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Refugee_Olympic_Team_at_the_2016_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I think it's pretty clear, I got stepped out on as I was about to kick in the home straight then, boom, the French lad took me down,' Mills said after the race.\", \"from\": 1140, \"to\": 1301, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Asked what he told Hay, Mills replied: 'Probably not allowed to say.'\", \"from\": 1303, \"to\": 1372, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Asked if he will appeal, Mills said: 'I have not seen anyone but I am pretty sure BA will put in an appeal, I hope.\", \"from\": 1374, \"to\": 1489, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1456, \"end\": 1458, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Airways\", \"score\": 0.9494516998499263, \"rank\": 0.04841536781062949, \"text\": \"BA\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q46970\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Airways\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Airways\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'From my perspective that was the perfect qualifier for me going through the first 2k in six minutes, I was like, 'alright, nobody in this field can run away from me in this pace'.\", \"from\": 1491, \"to\": 1671, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'So I was just sitting and biding my time, gonna to kick off the home straight and bang, hit the deck.\", \"from\": 1673, \"to\": 1775, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"What can you do?'\", \"from\": 1776, \"to\": 1793, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After the race, it was confirmed that Mills has now advanced to the next round following a decision from the race referee.\", \"from\": 1795, \"to\": 1917, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The three others fallers - Foppen, Ndikumwenayo and Lobalu have also been put through.\", \"from\": 1919, \"to\": 2005, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"When asked for his version of the collision with Mills, Hay said: 'I do not know what happened.\", \"from\": 2007, \"to\": 2102, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I did not feel anything.\", \"from\": 2103, \"to\": 2127, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I was surprised that George came to see me after the race, because I did not feel anything, well no more than usual.\", \"from\": 2128, \"to\": 2244, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'It pushed in the last 400m, it was really a massacre.\", \"from\": 2246, \"to\": 2300, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I turned around, there was no one left.\", \"from\": 2301, \"to\": 2340, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was incredible.\", \"from\": 2341, \"to\": 2359, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I have no idea what's going to happen, it scares me.\", \"from\": 2361, \"to\": 2414, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For me, it happened clearly.\", \"from\": 2415, \"to\": 2443, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That's what I said to George.\", \"from\": 2444, \"to\": 2473, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If I am guilty, sorry, but I think I was pushed.\", \"from\": 2474, \"to\": 2522, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not think I did anything wrong, but it scares me a little bit.\", \"from\": 2523, \"to\": 2590, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I hope it will work out and that I will be able to get into the final.\", \"from\": 2592, \"to\": 2663, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If ever the protest passes and I am eliminated, of course, it will hurt but I know that I had the level to qualify and that I have never been so strong.\", \"from\": 2664, \"to\": 2816, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For me, I am qualified, that's the most important thing.'\", \"from\": 2817, \"to\": 2874, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Paula Radcliffe, who was covering the race for the BBC, said after the race: 'There is a lot to look back at, I lot to tidy up and decide whose fault it was.\", \"from\": 2876, \"to\": 3033, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2876, \"end\": 2891, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paula_Radcliffe\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paula Radcliffe\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paula_Radcliffe\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paula_Radcliffe\"}, {\"begin\": 2927, \"end\": 2930, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"score\": 0.9997684208491171, \"rank\": 0.00023015122008485762, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'If you decide to jog that slightly, it's kind of your own fault.\", \"from\": 3035, \"to\": 3100, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You end up with all of those falls.'\", \"from\": 3101, \"to\": 3137, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"BBC pundit Steve Cram added: 'Paula's right to some extent, with the exception of Nordas most have got themselves to blame.\", \"from\": 3139, \"to\": 3262, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3139, \"end\": 3142, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"score\": 0.9997684208491171, \"rank\": 0.00023015122008485762, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\"}, {\"begin\": 3150, \"end\": 3160, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Steve_Cram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Steve Cram\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Steve_Cram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Steve_Cram\"}, {\"begin\": 3169, \"end\": 3174, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paula_of_Rome\", \"score\": 0.9969900004758335, \"rank\": 0.00301906926307382, \"text\": \"Paula\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paula_of_Rome\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paula_of_Rome\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'George was in a bad position from a long way out and should have checked out much earlier.'\", \"from\": 3264, \"to\": 3356, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Former Great Britain 400m runner, Allison Curbishley, said on BBC Radio 5 Live: 'George Mills has done this so many times, he does not put himself in the best of positions.\", \"from\": 3358, \"to\": 3530, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3365, \"end\": 3378, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9292992245557778, \"rank\": 0.06296259479409844, \"text\": \"Great Britain\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 3392, \"end\": 3410, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Allison_Curbishley\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Allison Curbishley\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Allison_Curbishley\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Allison_Curbishley\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'You are always going to get yourself caught up when when there is too many people.'\", \"from\": 3532, \"to\": 3616, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For more stories like this,check our sport page.\", \"from\": 3618, \"to\": 3666, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Metro Sport for the latest news onFacebook,TwitterandInstagram.\", \"from\": 3668, \"to\": 3738, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ArrowMORE:Team GB star fails to reach 'expected level' with shocking Olympic performance  ArrowMORE:Olympics star smashes European record and immediately proposes to partner  ArrowMORE:How many sports and medals are there at the Paris 2024 Olympics?\", \"from\": 3740, \"to\": 3989, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3862, \"end\": 3877, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UEFA\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.566304135945779e-22, \"text\": \"European record\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UEFA\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UEFA\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Your guide to the week in football.\", \"from\": 3991, \"to\": 4026, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Exclusive analysis, FPL tips and transfer talk - sign up, it's an open goal.\", \"from\": 4027, \"to\": 4103, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Let us know which team you support.Close  This site is protected by reCAPTCHA and theGoogle Privacy PolicyandTerms of Serviceapply.\", \"from\": 4105, \"to\": 4236, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Your information will be used in line with ourPrivacy Policy\", \"from\": 4237, \"to\": 4297, \"entities\": []}]}"